{"tid":836721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國務卿: 關注禁止香港民族黨運作","createTime":"2018-09-26T00:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T01:16:21.000Z","uid":62257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36302af54270aaf59ce147d061d1853019008c27","tid":836721,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:38:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180926/mobile/bkn-20180926014252081-0926_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180926%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180926014252081-0926_00822_001.html&d=K%2BiddrwNjGpv%2BTt7PTNmecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a2e3cbfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180926/mobile/bkn-20180926014252081-0926_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n港府周一（24日）刊憲禁止香港民族黨運作，美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）對此表達關注。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人諾爾特（Heather Nauert）周二在社交網站Twitter引述蓬佩奧稱，美方關注到港府禁止香港民族黨運作的決定，重申美國支持言論自由，以及和平集會、結社的自由，並指「這些是我們與香港共享的核心價值，必須極力捍衞。」&nbsp;"},{"pid":"c6a6638b17d862e9e5da4173dfb4f166123cf8cc","tid":836721,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T00:57:41.000Z","msg":"淋病再亂黎<br />\n會手尾長"},{"pid":"a3e04c38a3107068730e23e897384fa7afa7d4ed","tid":836721,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}